00:25:20,063 --> 00:25:21,375
Thank you so much.

288
00:25:21,485 --> 00:25:23,516
After I'm done with errands,

289
00:25:23,532 --> 00:25:25,172
I thought I'd go buy

290
00:25:25,180 --> 00:25:26,937
