298
00:25:40,759 --> 00:25:42,321
it won't take too long.

299
00:25:43,508 --> 00:25:44,708
Alright then.

300
00:26:00,401 --> 00:26:02,338
Drink a lot of water, Ms. Malai.

301
00:26:10,385 --> 00:26:11,940
Do you reckon it measures up

302
00:26:11,956 --> 00:26:13,604
