303
00:26:17,739 --> 00:26:18,739
Yes.

304
00:26:18,957 --> 00:26:20,246
Equally delightful.

305
00:26:23,645 --> 00:26:24,645
Oh,

306
00:26:24,825 --> 00:26:25,996
Kam, Uan, are there any

307
00:26:26,021 --> 00:26:27,473
