308
00:26:27,590 --> 00:26:29,160
I'll buy some for Mai.

309
00:26:32,973 --> 00:26:34,301
Don't be shy,

310
00:26:35,004 --> 00:26:36,020
I love Mai as my

311
00:26:36,043 --> 00:26:37,426
own child or grandchild.

312
00:26:37,747 --> 00:26:39,168
Tell me what you want.

313
00:26:41,955 --> 00:26:42,955
Umm..

314
00:26:43,744 --> 00:26:44,744
Well...

315
00:26:46,602 --> 00:26:47,602
Kam.

316
00:26:50,242 --> 00:26:51,242
Ms. Malai...

317
00:26:52,328 --> 00:26:54,250
What's the matter with both of you?

318
00:26:56,438 --> 00:26:57,718
I was simply...

319
00:27:03,212 --> 00:27:05,235
Is something wrong, Ms. Malai?

320
00:27:19,312 --> 00:27:20,328
Kam.

321
00:27:25,258 --> 00:27:26,258
Uan.

322
00:27:43,676 --> 00:27:44,676
Ms. Malai!

323
00:30:24,140 --> 00:30:25,929
Please forgive me, Ms. Malai.

324
00:30:26,110 --> 00:30:27,264
Uan and I truly

325
00:30:29,358 --> 00:30:30,694
had no other option.

326
00:30:35,837 --> 00:30:37,782
I'm deeply sorry, Ms. Malai.

327
00:30:38,142 --> 00:30:40,001
If you were to report the poisoning

328
00:30:40,026 --> 00:30:42,009
of the viscount to the authorities

329
00:30:44,165 --> 00:30:46,204
and we end up being sent to jail,

330
00:30:46,229 --> 00:30:47,930
who would look after Mai then?

331
00:30:49,040 --> 00:30:50,970
Please understand our predicament.

332
00:30:55,751 --> 00:30:56,751
Stand up.

333
00:30:56,900 --> 00:30:57,900
Come.

334
00:30:59,829 --> 00:31:01,157
There's no time to cry.

335
00:31:01,173 --> 00:31:03,524
Let's proceed with the plan quickly. Go!

