354
00:42:16,679 --> 00:42:18,999
I'm sorry, Young Master Mueang.

355
00:42:26,367 --> 00:42:27,367
Let's go!

356
00:42:28,226 --> 00:42:30,585
Kam! Uan!

357
00:42:31,109 --> 00:42:33,007
Do you know that the house is on fire

358
00:42:33,070 --> 00:42:34,890
