361
00:42:40,164 --> 00:42:41,616
You didn't tell me anything.

362
00:42:42,725 --> 00:42:44,343
Head to the boat first.

363
00:42:44,359 --> 00:42:45,479
- Yes.
- Hurry.

364
00:42:46,092 --> 00:42:47,601
Did you not hear what I said?

365
00:42:47,804 --> 00:42:50,338
Come and help out now! There's a fire!

366
00:42:55,007 --> 00:42:56,194
