372
00:43:16,023 --> 00:43:17,023
I'm sorry!

373
00:43:18,125 --> 00:43:19,038
Do not interfere!

374
00:43:19,921 --> 00:43:20,921
Kam!

375
00:43:22,093 --> 00:43:23,453
