00:45:35,640 --> 00:45:36,819
Ms. Malai showed me

394
00:45:36,828 --> 00:45:38,508
everything that happened.

395
00:45:38,742 --> 00:45:39,859
She insists that you were

396
00:45:39,867 --> 00:45:41,023
the one who harmed her.

397
00:45:41,039 --> 00:45:42,319
You betrayed me!

398
00:45:42,953 --> 00:45:43,953
Whoa!

399
00:45:45,273 --> 00:45:46,273
Whoa!

